<paragraph pageNumber="523">measurements (mm) Lectotype major: HW 0.84, HL 0.90, SL 0.42, EL 0.08, PW 0.40.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="523">Paralectotype minor: HW 0.38, HL 0.44, SL 0.38, EL 0.06, PW 0.24.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="523">color Major: concolorous clear medium yellow, except for gaster and appendages, which are light yellow. Minor: concolorous pale yellow.</paragraph>
